hello I'm Fatma a technical specialist
here at the AWS office in Cape Town
today I'll show you how to update the
telephone number that's associated with
your AWS account let's get
started first log to the AWS Management
console as the root user or an IM am
user with the administrator access then
choose your username in the top right
corner and then select account next to
contact information choose edit in the
edit contact information page update the
phone number filled with the new
telephone number that you want
associated with the account make sure
that the phone number includes the
correct country code and that it does
not have Extra Spaces or special
characters for example if you update a
UK number such as 079
111123 456 enter it as +44
23456 after you update the number choose
update at the
bottom the telephone number that's
associated with your AWS account is now
updated please note to make sure that
you update this contact information
regularly AWS uses this number when it's
necessary to reach you about account and
buing matters so now now you know how to
update the telephone number that's
associated with your AWS
account thanks for watching and happy
cloud computing from all of us here at
AWS
[Applause]
[Music]
